01:03:07.730 --> 01:03:09.240 align:middle line:90%
I'm not going there.

01:03:09.240 --> 01:03:10.850 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to my soul.

01:03:10.850 --> 01:03:13.030 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to ground both of us.

01:03:13.030 --> 01:03:15.070 align:middle line:84%
There's a contagion there
that's more powerful.

01:03:15.070 --> 01:03:17.450 align:middle line:84%
>> When I went there, I
strictly went there for physical

01:03:17.450 --> 01:03:19.550 align:middle line:90%
purposes I thought.

01:03:19.550 --> 01:03:21.320 align:middle line:90%
But there's something about him.

01:03:21.320 --> 01:03:25.040 align:middle line:84%
When you walk in his office,
he knows who you are,

01:03:25.040 --> 01:03:27.650 align:middle line:90%
not your mind, not your story.

01:03:27.650 --> 01:03:29.540 align:middle line:84%
He knows the essence
of your being,

01:03:29.540 --> 01:03:31.520 align:middle line:84%
and right away the
healing starts.

01:03:31.520 --> 01:03:35.340 align:middle line:84%
I was living thinking, well, I
came from messed up background.

01:03:35.340 --> 01:03:36.800 align:middle line:90%
I blamed it on everybody.

01:03:36.800 --> 01:03:39.470 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't know what
the root of it was.

01:03:39.470 --> 01:03:42.620 align:middle line:84%
>> So self contempt is
something that's been programmed

01:03:42.620 --> 01:03:44.120 align:middle line:90%
in our lives.

01:03:44.120 --> 01:03:46.790 align:middle line:90%
We tend to feel shame, doubt.

01:03:46.790 --> 01:03:50.180 align:middle line:84%
We tend to feel negative
feelings about the concept

01:03:50.180 --> 01:03:53.510 align:middle line:90%
of self being deserving.

01:03:53.510 --> 01:03:56.570 align:middle line:84%
I would say, I want you to
picture yourself as a child.

01:03:56.570 --> 01:03:59.420 align:middle line:84%
Go home and search through
all your photographs.

01:03:59.420 --> 01:04:02.485 align:middle line:84%
Find yourself as a five-year-old
kid, a six-year-old kid.

01:04:02.485 --> 01:04:04.610 align:middle line:84%
And look at that picture
that five or six-year-old,

01:04:04.610 --> 01:04:06.710 align:middle line:84%
and there's two things
I wanted to look for,

01:04:06.710 --> 01:04:09.410 align:middle line:90%
deservedness and innocence.

01:04:09.410 --> 01:04:13.850 align:middle line:84%
After years and years
of living in this world,

01:04:13.850 --> 01:04:16.370 align:middle line:90%
we tend to lose the innocence.

01:04:16.370 --> 01:04:19.790 align:middle line:84%
We tend to lose the
sense of deservedness.

01:04:19.790 --> 01:04:23.000 align:middle line:84%
We associate our deservedness
with our innocence.

01:04:23.000 --> 01:04:26.660 align:middle line:84%
So can we associate deservedness
with the loss of innocence?

01:04:26.660 --> 01:04:28.100 align:middle line:90%
That's extremely important.

01:04:28.100 --> 01:04:30.730 align:middle line:84%
And we forgive ourselves
for growing up.

01:04:30.730 --> 01:04:33.650 align:middle line:84%
To really overcome
dis-ease, we have

01:04:33.650 --> 01:04:36.970 align:middle line:84%
to be willing to embrace
and forgive ourselves

01:04:36.970 --> 01:04:42.370 align:middle line:84%
for being adults and to love
ourselves at a core level,

01:04:42.370 --> 01:04:43.630 align:middle line:90%
not at an ego level.

01:04:43.630 --> 01:04:45.640 align:middle line:84%
We don't want to love
ourselves conditionally.

01:04:45.640 --> 01:04:46.930 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not talking
about loving yourself

01:04:46.930 --> 01:04:48.130 align:middle line:90%
because you won the lottery.

01:04:48.130 --> 01:04:52.035 align:middle line:84%
I'm talking about having a
core love of that child that

01:04:52.035 --> 01:04:53.410 align:middle line:84%
was five and six
years old that's

01:04:53.410 --> 01:04:54.920 align:middle line:90%
still living in your heart.

01:04:54.920 --> 01:04:59.170 align:middle line:84%
>> He would do that work on
me to go in and really nurture

01:04:59.170 --> 01:05:00.260 align:middle line:90%
myself.

01:05:00.260 --> 01:05:03.730 align:middle line:84%
So I was able to reflect on
the kindness that I do have,

01:05:03.730 --> 01:05:06.070 align:middle line:90%
the tenderness, the love.

01:05:06.070 --> 01:05:08.290 align:middle line:84%
And all he wanted me to do
was, instead of putting it

01:05:08.290 --> 01:05:11.610 align:middle line:84%
all on the outside, was to take
it in and put it on the inside.

01:05:11.610 --> 01:05:14.770 align:middle line:84%
I got off the
cocaine, didn't drink.

01:05:14.770 --> 01:05:18.400 align:middle line:84%
But sugar was the
essence of an addiction

01:05:18.400 --> 01:05:20.350 align:middle line:90%
that, again, I was a little kid.

01:05:20.350 --> 01:05:21.370 align:middle line:90%
I'm three years old.

01:05:21.370 --> 01:05:22.390 align:middle line:90%
I had a tooth pulled.

01:05:22.390 --> 01:05:24.130 align:middle line:90%
They gave me a lollipop.

01:05:24.130 --> 01:05:25.005 align:middle line:90%
I did something else.

01:05:25.005 --> 01:05:25.805 align:middle line:90%
I fell down.

01:05:25.805 --> 01:05:27.010 align:middle line:90%
A doctor gave me ice cream.

01:05:27.010 --> 01:05:29.260 align:middle line:90%
So for me, sugar was nurturing.

01:05:29.260 --> 01:05:31.900 align:middle line:84%
It was loving, and
little did I know what

01:05:31.900 --> 01:05:33.790 align:middle line:90%
