01:05:33.790 --> 01:05:36.040 align:middle line:84%
I was getting progressively
sick again and just

01:05:36.040 --> 01:05:37.630 align:middle line:84%
filled with mucus,
to a point where

01:05:37.630 --> 01:05:38.800 align:middle line:90%
I thought I had pneumonia.

01:05:38.800 --> 01:05:40.970 align:middle line:84%
It was horrible, and
I lived like that.

01:05:40.970 --> 01:05:42.100 align:middle line:90%
And I thought I was dying.

01:05:42.100 --> 01:05:43.475 align:middle line:84%
And he kept saying,
Diane, you've

01:05:43.475 --> 01:05:44.908 align:middle line:90%
got to give up the sugar.

01:05:44.908 --> 01:05:45.950 align:middle line:90%
You've got to give it up.

01:05:45.950 --> 01:05:50.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Addiction is
compensation for hurt.

01:05:50.830 --> 01:05:55.210 align:middle line:84%
I have a hole in my
heart that doesn't heal.

01:05:55.210 --> 01:05:59.050 align:middle line:84%
Addiction takes
sugar, love, money,

01:05:59.050 --> 01:06:01.450 align:middle line:84%
whatever from the
outside and attempts

01:06:01.450 --> 01:06:04.720 align:middle line:84%
to patch up that hole in
the heart, which lasts

01:06:04.720 --> 01:06:06.310 align:middle line:90%
for a short period of time.

01:06:06.310 --> 01:06:09.160 align:middle line:84%
To heal the heart
from the inside out

01:06:09.160 --> 01:06:12.950 align:middle line:84%
is to occupy your own heart
with your consciousness,

01:06:12.950 --> 01:06:17.360 align:middle line:84%
to venture and journey into your
own heart, to admit the pain,

01:06:17.360 --> 01:06:20.642 align:middle line:84%
to acknowledge the pain,
to confront the pain,

01:06:20.642 --> 01:06:25.300 align:middle line:84%
to feel the pain
all the way through.

01:06:25.300 --> 01:06:27.610 align:middle line:84%
>> That pain transformed
things in me,

01:06:27.610 --> 01:06:34.450 align:middle line:84%
where I have been reconnecting
with letting go of the fight.

01:06:34.450 --> 01:06:36.790 align:middle line:84%
>> Some people can be
addicted to substances.

01:06:36.790 --> 01:06:38.800 align:middle line:84%
They can be addicted
to behaviors.

01:06:38.800 --> 01:06:41.050 align:middle line:84%
I think control is one of
the most powerful addictions

01:06:41.050 --> 01:06:42.050 align:middle line:90%
that I see every day.

01:06:42.050 --> 01:06:43.892 align:middle line:84%
One of most powerful
healing agents

01:06:43.892 --> 01:06:45.850 align:middle line:84%
is when people finally
get clear about the fact

01:06:45.850 --> 01:06:48.560 align:middle line:84%
