they support flow and not

01:06:48.560 --> 01:06:49.360 align:middle line:90%
resistance.

01:06:49.360 --> 01:06:50.500 align:middle line:90%
>> I would cry a lot.

01:06:50.500 --> 01:06:52.880 align:middle line:84%
I would feel, and I
didn't even want to feel.

01:06:52.880 --> 01:06:56.050 align:middle line:84%
I certainly didn't want to
cry in an office like that.

