01:07:11.590 --> 01:07:12.430 align:middle line:90%
And I gave up sugar.

01:07:12.430 --> 01:07:15.610 align:middle line:84%
I haven't had sugar,
other than some fruit,

01:07:15.610 --> 01:07:18.250 align:middle line:84%
in eight or 10 years,
which is a miracle.

01:07:18.250 --> 01:07:21.910 align:middle line:84%
I knew I could go somewhere
where somebody unconditionally

01:07:21.910 --> 01:07:26.260 align:middle line:84%
cared about me and was willing
to hold the space until I

01:07:26.260 --> 01:07:27.580 align:middle line:90%
caught up with it.

01:07:27.580 --> 01:07:29.560 align:middle line:84%
If I didn't have Mark
Mincolla in my life,

01:07:29.560 --> 01:07:32.720 align:middle line:84%
and I just went to a
psychiatrist, a regular one,

01:07:32.720 --> 01:07:34.450 align:middle line:90%
or I went to a regular doctor--

01:07:34.450 --> 01:07:35.500 align:middle line:90%
not putting them down.

01:07:35.500 --> 01:07:38.450 align:middle line:84%
Everybody has their
purpose, but in my life,

01:07:38.450 --> 01:07:41.070 align:middle line:90%
I don't think I'd be here today.

